{"id":574767,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/12/【立此存照】颂歌新赛季•校园篇（二）少先队员/","date":"2017-12-18T08:04:18Z","modified":"2017-12-18T09:17:11Z","title":"【立此存照】颂歌新赛季•校园篇（二）少先队员要热爱伟大领袖","content":"<p><strong>相关阅读：中国数字空间｜<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%B4%87%E6%8B%9C#.E3.80.90.E7.AB.8B.E6.AD.A4.E5.AD.98.E7.85.A7.E3.80.91.E9.A2.82.E6.AD.8C.E6.96.B0.E8.B5.9B.E5.AD.A3.E2.80.A2.E6.A0.A1.E5.9B.AD.E7.AF.87.EF.BC.88.E4.B8.80.EF\">颂歌新赛季</a></strong></p>\n<p>12月13日上午，团中央书记处书记、全国少工委主任傅振邦同志到北京市丰台区第五小学科丰校区调研少先队工作，参加“争做新时代好队员”主题队会活动，向少先队员宣讲党的十九大精神。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-574768\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/640-3-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"367\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/640-3-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/640-3.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>傅振邦指出，少先队员学习了解党的十九大，重点要记住三句话：中国共产党是伟大的党，我们所处的新时代是伟大的时代，习近平爷爷是伟大的领袖。少先队员要牢记习爷爷的关怀和教导，拥抱新时代，争做好队员，听党的话、跟党走。</p>\n<p>傅振邦说，少先队员要记住，习近平爷爷是伟大的领袖。习爷爷从党的十八大以来成为我们党的领袖、国家的元首，过去五年领导全党全国人民取得了极不平凡的巨大成绩。……少先队员一定要知道，今天我们有伟大的领袖习近平爷爷是国之大幸，在他的领导下，我们党会越来越强大，我们的国家会越来越强大，我们中国会越来越多的为全世界做出自己更大的贡献。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>参见<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/ln9i9OPBjsbgPo4j6500VA\">报道全文</a>。</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>来源：全国少工委办公室</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>相关资讯：</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-574802\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/DQMEpzFUQAIa0wc-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/DQMEpzFUQAIa0wc-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/DQMEpzFUQAIa0wc-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/DQMEpzFUQAIa0wc-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/DQMEpzFUQAIa0wc.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-574769\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/IMG_3318-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/IMG_3318-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/IMG_3318-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/IMG_3318-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/IMG_3318.jpg 1440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_574770\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-574770\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/96788B53-5196-4DB2-ABCF-2CD311F6842C-948-0000012109551F76_tmp-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/96788B53-5196-4DB2-ABCF-2CD311F6842C-948-0000012109551F76_tmp-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/96788B53-5196-4DB2-ABCF-2CD311F6842C-948-0000012109551F76_tmp-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/96788B53-5196-4DB2-ABCF-2CD311F6842C-948-0000012109551F76_tmp-768x768.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/96788B53-5196-4DB2-ABCF-2CD311F6842C-948-0000012109551F76_tmp-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/12/96788B53-5196-4DB2-ABCF-2CD311F6842C-948-0000012109551F76_tmp.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">图片来自网络</p></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/12/%E3%80%90%E7%AB%8B%E6%AD%A4%E5%AD%98%E7%85%A7%E3%80%91%E9%A2%82%E6%AD%8C%E6%96%B0%E8%B5%9B%E5%AD%A3%E2%80%A2%E6%A0%A1%E5%9B%AD%E7%AF%87%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%E7%94%A8%E4%B9%A0%E6%80%9D%E6%83%B3/\">【立此存照】颂歌新赛季•校园篇（一）用习思想指导数学</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1052,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,28589,